
DSKCLR has been modified to accept a mode and parameters:

	DSKCLR	<mode>,
	 <params>
	 error return
	normal return

where <mode> = :
	0  dc.clr	clear in-core disk info
	1  dc.fpc	set STTPFC for all sats, clear SRPNDS
	2  dc.nds	clear SRPNDS

and the <params> corressponding to each <mode> are:
	0  no <params>
	1  addr of AOBJN word of form
	     -no. of args,,addr of first arg
	2  no <params>
